            <p>Scout, sign, and develop a roster of originals. Build factions around alliances and competing agendas &mdash; then decide who teams up, who splits off, and whose banner is flying when the city&rsquo;s biggest matches get booked. Loyalty, like everything in this business, is negotiable.</p>
